If you wish to simplify/modify/explore the expression, it&#39;s been explained on the top right panel of [regex101.com](https://regex101.com/r/vjYzYR/1/). If you&#39;d like, you can also watch in [this link](https://regex101.com/r/vjYzYR/1/debugger), how it would match against some sample inputs.

